high_descs: Turn around and move so you are directly in front of the tv facing it.
Pick up the pen on the edge of the bottom shelf of the tv stand.
Turn left and go to the space between the dining room table and the couch.
Put the pen on the white plate nearest the right corner of the table.
Pick up the plate with the pen on it.
Turn right and move around the couch to the table in front of the couch.
Put the plate with the pen on it on top of the table in front of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a pen on it on a table.

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk straight, then turn right to face the television.
Pick the pen up off of the TV stand.
Turn around, walk around the sofa and face the dining table.
Place the pen on the dish on the table.
Pick up the dish with the pen on it.
Turn around, walk around the couch and face the coffee table.
Place the dish with the pen on it on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place the pen on the dish on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk around the front side of the couch to get to the TV stand.
Pick up the pen on the bottom shelf.
Turn around and go around the back side of the couch to the table.
Put the pen on the rightmost plate.
Pick up the plate.
Turn around and go around the front of the couch to the coffee table.
Put the plate on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a pen on it on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn right to walk around the furniture. Locate the TV on the far side of the room.
Pick up the pen from the bottom shelf of the table.
Carry the pen and turn to the left, then the left again to go to the dinning table.
Put the pen on the plate to the front right of the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Carry the plate and turn around and go to the right past the couch.
Place the pen and plate on the square table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pen and plate to the table.

high_descs: Turn around, turn right, turn right past the sofa and then work your way left until you are facing the TV
Pick up a pencil off of the TV stand
Head left, past the couch and stand at the end of the dinner table facing a plate
Place the pencil on the plate
Pick up the plate with the pencil on it
Go back past the sofa and turn to face the coffee table
Drop the plate with the pencil on it on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with the pencil on it on a coffee table
